1 olive oil
1 cucumber
1 apple
1 packet roasted almonds
1 bag herbs
1 bag salad leaves
1 packet Grated Parmesan Cheese

• Thinly slice cucumber into half-moons. Thinly slice apple into wedges.

• Roughly chop roasted almonds and herbs.

• In a medium bowl, combine salad leaves, grated Parmesan cheese, cucumber, apple, a pinch of salt and pepper and a drizzle of olive oil.

• Transfer apple and Parmesan green salad to a serving dish. Drizzle with some balsamic glaze.
• Sprinkle with almonds and herbs to serve. Enjoy!